Subject: Upgrade to Latest Version - StealthAudit
Description: Can we schedule a time to upgrade to the latest version and do a health check?
Solution_Comment__c:
We uninstalled StealthAUDIT version 11.5.0.240 and installed the 11.6.0.82 version.
We uninstalled the Access Information Center version 11.5.0.130 and installed the 11.6.0.21 version.
We deleted the old cert and assigned the new cert. We have also ensured the customer can access the AIC portal and the Publish Report site.
